<div class="ui segments">
    <div class="ui inverted segment">
        <h1>Teamz Generator</h1>
        <div class="ui accordion">
            <div class="title">
                <i class=" inverted dropdown icon"></i>
                <span class="ui inverted grey text">What is TEAMZ?</span>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                <p>
                    TEAMZ is a friendly, yet competitive, impromptu Time Attack event where a group of players are split up into equally sized random or drafted teams. Each team will generally have around 10 minutes to prepare, before spending an hour or so TAing a random quest. Obviously, the team with the best time at the cutoff is the victor.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="title">
                <i class=" inverted dropdown icon"></i>
                <span class="ui inverted grey text">Why TEAMZ?</span>
            </div>
            <div class="content">
                <p>
                    TEAMZ emphasizes quick planning and coordination between party members that may not be familiar with each others' playstyles. Additionally, the quest selected may be unfamiliar to the players; this forces players to learn new quests and tests each player's ability to memorize enemy spawns in a time-constrained environment. Thanks 98.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="ui hidden divider"></div>
    <div class="ui inverted segment grid">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="three wide column">
                <div id="party_count" class="ui inverted selection dropdown">
                    <input type="hidden" name="party_count" value="2">
                    <i class="dropdown icon"></i>
                    <div class="default text">Party Count</div>
                    <div class="menu">
                        <div class="item" data-value="2">2 Players</div>
                        <div class="item" data-value="3">3 Players</div>
                        <div class="item" data-value="4">4 Players</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="three wide column">
                <div id="class_mixer" class="ui inverted checkbox">
                    <input type="checkbox" name="class_mixer">
                    <label>Class Mixer</label>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="three wide column">
                <div id="challenge_mode" class="ui inverted checkbox">
                    <input type="checkbox" name="challenge_mode">
                    <label>Challenge Mode</label>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="column">
                <div id="quest_list" class="ui inverted loading fluid search multiple selection dropdown">
                    <i class="dropdown icon"></i>
                    <div class="default text">Excluded Quests...</div>
                    <div class="menu"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="column">
                <div id="player_list" class="ui inverted fluid search multiple selection dropdown">
                    <div class="default text">Players...</div>
                    <div class="menu"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="three wide column">
                <button class="ui inverted fluid button" id="generate_quest">
                    Generate Quest
                </button>
            </div>
            <div class="three wide column">
                <button class="ui inverted fluid button" id="generate_parties">
                    Generate Parties
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="ui hidden divider"></div>
    <div class="ui inverted segment">
        <h3 id="quest_name"></h3>
        <div class="ui hidden divider"></div>
        <div id="party_list" class="ui three stackable cards"></div>
    </div>
</div>
<%- js('js/teamz-generator.js') %>
